{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"reuseIdentifier","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A unique string identifier for this view that allows you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to reuse this view with multiple similar annotations. You can set this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameter to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if you don’t intend to reuse the view, but it is a good"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"idea in general to specify a reuse identifier to avoid creating redundant"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views."}]}],"name":"reuseIdentifier"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The initialized annotation view object."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The reuse identifier provides a way for you to improve performance by recycling"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation views as they enter and leave the map’s viewport. As an annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"leaves the viewport, the map view moves its associated view to a reuse queue."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When a new annotation becomes visible, you can request a view for that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation by passing the appropriate reuse identifier string to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"},{"type":"text","text":" method."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L77"},"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)initWithReuseIdentifier:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/initWithReuseIdentifier:"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreuseidentifier:"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a reusable annotation view object associated with its identifier."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/dequeuereusableannotationviewwithidentifier:","title":"dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/dequeueReusableAnnotationViewWithIdentifier:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/initWithReuseIdentifier:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Initializes and returns a new annotation view object."}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"initWithReuseIdentifier:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/initwithreu